**GST (Goods and Services Tax)** is India's unified indirect tax that replaced VAT, service tax, and excise duty. The current GST rates are 0%, 5%, 12%, 18%, and 28% depending on the category of goods or services. This calculator helps you compute the GST amount on any transaction and find the price before tax from an inclusive price.
